WHAT DO YOU FEAR?
Do you fear me?
No, I do not!
Do you fear anyone?
No, I do not fear anyone! !
You want to know who I fear?
I fear God!
He looks at me from
above everyday!
He watches every step you do!
Sometimes life isn't easy when you
want to do something your not supposed to.
God who is above you,
helping you and telling
you to do the right thing.
So, when someone tells you
Is their anyone you fear in the world?
Answer with a simple easy answer.
Yes, I fear God.
He will always be by your side
no matter where and what you are doing.

